reviewText: I think that this movie is a nice movie because it has a bear cub that likes a girl.
What a great family story!  Those bears are so cute, but the message is still there.  My kids know now that bears are wild and we must protect there homes or no more bears!

Great Family Movie! My girls LOVE it and want to watch Masha and Emily constantly!
We really enjoyed this movie & the scenery & bears . A nice story with great soundtrack . Recommended to all . The bears & other animals are great & a credit to the trainers .
